{This is a very instructive game that shows the typical ideas after an f2-f4 idea.} 1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. cxd5 cxd5 5. Bf4 Nc6 6. e3 e6 7. Bd3 Bd6 8. Bxd6 Qxd6 9. f4 O-O 10. Nf3 a6 11. O-O b5 12. Ne5 Bb7 13. Qf3 Ne7 14. g4 b4 15. g5 Ne8 16. Ne2 f5 17. gxf6 Nxf6 18. Ng3 Rac8 19. Rf2 g6 20. h4 Nf5 21. Nxf5 exf5 22. Rg2 Kh8 23. Kh2 Bc6 24. Rag1 Be8 25. Rg5 Nd7 26. h5 Nxe5 27. fxe5 Qe7 28. hxg6 hxg6 29. Qh3+ Qh7 30. R1g3 Rc6 31. Qxh7+ Kxh7 32. Rh3+ Kg7 33. Kg3 Rh8 34. Rxh8 Kxh8 35. Kf4 Kg7 36. Bxf5 Rc1 37. Bd3 Ra1 38. Bxa6 Rxa2 39. Bb7 Rxb2 40. Bxd5 Rf2+ 41. Kg3 Re2 42. Kf3 Rd2 43. Rg1 b3 44. Bxb3 Bc6+ 45. Kg3 Rd3 46. Bc2 Rxe3+ 47. Kf2 Rc3 48. Rxg6+ Kf7 49. Bf5 Bd5 50. Rf6+ Ke7 51. Rd6 Rf3+ 52. Ke2 Rxf5 53. Rxd5 Rf4 54. Ke3 Rh4 55. Ra5 Ke6 56. Ra6+ Ke7 57. Kd3 Rh1 58. Ke4 Rb1 59. Rc6 Rb5 60. Rc5 Rb1 61. Kd5 Ra1 62. Rc7+ Kd8 63. Rh7 Ra5+ 64. Ke6 Ra6+ 65. Kf5 Ra1 66. d5 Ra6 67. d6 1-0

