1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Bf4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Nc6 6. e3 a6 7. Bd3 g6 $2 {Black plans to fianchetto the dark-squared bishop which won't contribute to the battle on the queenside, so this is offering White a free hand on that side of the board.} 8. h3 Bg7 9. Nf3 O-O 10. Rc1 Qb6 (10... b5 11. O-O Bb7 12. a4 b4 13. Nb1 $14) (10... Nb4 11. Bb1 b6 12. O-O Bb7 13. Ne5 $16) 11. Qe2 Nb4 12. Bb1 Bd7 13. O-O (13. Ne5 $1 $16) 13... Ne4 14. Rfd1 $16 Nxc3 15. bxc3 Nc6 16. e4 $1 e6 (16... dxe4 17. Bxe4 $16) 17. Bd3 Rfe8 18. Rb1 Qa7 19. e5 Rac8 20. Qd2 (20. Nh2 $5 {This move is also good.} h5 21. g4 hxg4 22. Nxg4 $18) 20... Ne7 21. g4 $6 (21. Bh6 Bh8 (21... Nf5 22. Bxg7 Kxg7 23. g4 (23. Nh2 h5 24. g4 hxg4 25. hxg4 $18) 23... Ne7 24. h4 $18) 22. Bg5 $18) 21... Rc7 22. Bh6 Bb5 23. Qf4 Bxd3 24. Bxg7 $6 (24. Rxd3 Bh8 25. Ng5 Nc6 26. Rf3 b5 27. h4 $18) 24... Kxg7 25. Qf6+ Kg8 26. Rxd3 Nc6 27. Qf4 Qb8 28. Ne1 (28. h4 Qd8 29. h5 Rf8 30. Qh6 f6 31. hxg6 hxg6 32. Ng5 fxg5 33. Rh3 $18) 28... Qd8 29. Rf3 Qe7 30. h4 Rec8 31. Nd3 $132 1/2-1/2

