1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Bf4 Nc6 5. e3 Bf5 6. Nc3 Nf6 7. Qb3 Na5 (7... Qb6 8. Qxb6 axb6 9. Bb5 $14) (7... Qd7 8. Nf3 e6 9. Ne5 Nxe5 $2 10. dxe5 $18 {[%csl Rf6][%cal Gf1b5]}) 8. Qa4+ Bd7 9. Qc2 Rc8 10. Nf3 g6 (10... Ne4 11. Bd3 Nxc3 12. bxc3 $14) 11. Bd3 Bg7 12. O-O O-O 13. Qe2 $1 (13. h3 Ne4 14. Bxe4 dxe4 15. Qxe4 $2 Rxc3 $1 16. bxc3 Bf5 $19 {This is what I calculated.}) 13... Bf5 (13... Bg4 14. h3 Bxf3 15. Qxf3 Nc4 16. Qe2 $14) (13... Nc4 14. Bxc4 (14. Nxd5 {May not be so good after:} Nxd5 15. Bxc4 Nxf4 16. exf4 Bg4) 14... Rxc4 15. Nxd5 (15. Ne5 Rc8)) 14. Bxf5 gxf5 15. Rac1 $1 Ne4 16. Nxe4 fxe4 $6 {Black has some weaknesses on the kingside since the e4-pawn should have been on g6, protecting the king.} 17. Ne5 $16 f6 $2 18. Qg4 $3 $16 {Black missed this move in the game, so I have a big advantage now.} f5 (18... Rxc1 19. Rxc1 Kh8 {Isn't possible due to:} (19... fxe5 20. Bxe5 Rf7 21. Rc8 $18) 20. Nf7+ $1 $18) (18... Rxc1 19. Bh6 Rxf1+ 20. Kxf1 Rf7 21. Nxf7 Qf8 (21... Kxf7 22. Qxg7+ Ke8 23. Qg8+ Kd7 24. Qxd5+ $18) 22. Bxg7 Qxg7 23. Nh6+ Kf8 24. Qc8#) (18... Kh8 19. Nf7+ $18) 19. Qg3 Rf6 (19... Kh8 20. Qh4 $1 e6 (20... Kg8 21. Rxc8 Qxc8 22. Qxe7) 21. Ng6+ Kg8 22. Ne7+ (22. Qxd8 $18)) (19... Rxc1 20. Bh6 (20. Rxc1 $18) 20... Rxf1+ 21. Kxf1 Rf7 22. Nxf7 Kxf7 23. Qxg7+ $18) 20. Bg5 Rxc1 21. Rxc1 Rd6 22. Qf4 Nc6 23. Nxc6 Rxc6 $6 (23... bxc6 $18) 24. Rxc6 bxc6 25. Qxf5 Qd6 26. Qc8+ Kf7 27. Qb7 $1 a5 (27... c5 28. Bf4 Qe6 29. dxc5 d4 30. exd4 Bxd4 31. h3 Bxc5 (31... e3 32. Bxe3 Bxe3 33. Qf3+ $18) 32. Qb5 $18) 28. h3 $1 Qb4 29. Qxc6 Qc4 30. Qb7 (30. Qxc4 $18) 30... Bf6 31. Bxf6 Kxf6 32. Qb6+ e6 33. Qxa5 Qc1+ 34. Kh2 Qxb2 35. Qd8+ Kf7 36. Qd7+ Kf6 37. Qxh7 Qxf2 38. Qh6+ Ke7 (38... Kf7 39. Qf4+ Qxf4+ 40. exf4 Kf6 41. g4 e3 42. Kg3 $18) 39. Qg5+ Kd7 40. Qg7+ Ke8 41. Qh6 Kd7 42. a4 Qa2 43. Qg7+ Ke8 44. Qf6 Kd7 45. Qf7+ Kd6 46. Qa7 Qd2 47. Qb8+ Kd7 48. Qf4 Qa5 49. Qf7+ $1 Kd6 50. h4 Qxa4 51. h5 Qb3 (51... Qa8 52. h6 Qh8 53. h7 e5 54. Qg8 Qf6 55. h8=Q $18) (51... Qd1 52. h6 Qg4 53. Qf4+ Qxf4+ 54. exf4 e3 55. Kg1 $18) 52. h6 Qxe3 53. Qf8+ Kd7 54. h7 1-0

