{Ivanov showed a great endgame technique in this game!} 1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Bf4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Nc6 6. e3 a6 7. Bd3 Bg4 8. Nge2 e6 9. O-O Bd6 10. Bxd6 Qxd6 11. Rc1 {If possible, White avoids playing the move f3.} Bh5 12. Na4 Nd7 13. Qb3 Rb8 (13... Na5 14. Qc3 $14) 14. Nc5 Nxc5 15. Rxc5 Bg6 16. Rfc1 (16. Nf4 Nxd4 {White needs to be careful of this tactic.}) 16... Bxd3 (16... O-O 17. Bxg6 hxg6 18. Qc3 Rfc8 19. Nf4 Ne7 20. Nd3 $14) 17. Qxd3 O-O 18. Nf4 {The knight is heading to the d3-square.} Rfc8 19. Qc3 Qd8 20. Nd3 Na7 21. a4 Rxc5 (21... b6 $2 22. Rc7 $18 {Black can barely move.}) 22. Qxc5 Nc8 (22... Nc6 23. b4 (23. Ne5 Rc8 (23... Nxe5 24. dxe5)) 23... Rc8 24. b5 axb5 25. Qxb5 $1 $16 (25. axb5 Ne7 $11) 25... Qe7 26. h3 $16 h6 27. Qb6 $16) 23. Qc7 Nd6 24. Kf1 Nc4 25. Qxd8+ Rxd8 26. Ke2 Rc8 27. f3 (27. b3 Nd6 28. Rxc8+ Nxc8 29. Nc5 Nd6 30. Kd3 a5 31. e4 dxe4+ $2 32. Nxe4 Nxe4 33. Kxe4 Kf8 34. Kd3 $1 $18 {[%cal Gd3c4,Gc4b5]}) 27... a5 28. e4 Nd6 29. Rxc8+ Nxc8 30. b4 b6 $6 (30... axb4 31. Nxb4 Ne7 32. Kd3 $14 (32. exd5 exd5 33. Nd3 Nc6 34. Kd2 Nxd4 35. Nc5 $14)) 31. b5 {With perfect play, this endgame is a draw. White demonstrates an amazing technique and wins this endgame.} Kf8 32. Nf4 Ne7 33. Ke3 g6 $6 (33... Ke8 34. g4 Kd8 35. Nh5 g6 36. Nf6 h6 37. Kf4 $18) 34. g4 (34. h4 $14) 34... Kg7 $2 (34... dxe4 35. fxe4 $14) 35. h4 h6 36. g5 hxg5 37. hxg5 {If Black captures dxe4, after fxe4, White would push d5 and will have a passed pawn, otherwise if Black doesn't capture on e4, White can continue with Nd3, Kf4, Ke5, and so on.} Kf8 (37... Kg8 38. Nd3 $18 (38. Ke2 Kf8 39. Ke3 Kg7 40. Nd3 $1 f6 41. Kf4 $18 Kf7 42. gxf6 Kxf6 43. Ne5 g5+ 44. Kg4 Nc8 45. Nc6 Kg6 46. e5 Kh6 47. Nd8 Na7 48. Nxe6 Nxb5 49. axb5 a4 50. Nc5 bxc5 51. b6 a3 52. b7 a2 53. b8=Q a1=Q 54. Kf5 $3 $18 {It's mate in six!})) 38. Nd3 dxe4 (38... Nc8 39. exd5 exd5 40. Kf4 $18) (38... Kg7 $6 39. Ne5 Kg8 40. Nd7 Nc8 41. exd5 exd5 42. Kf4 $18) 39. fxe4 Nc8 40. Ne5 Ke7 41. Nc4 $3 Kd7 (41... f6 42. gxf6+ Kxf6 43. Kf4 g5+ 44. Kg4 Kg6 45. e5 Ne7 (45... Kh6 46. Nd6 Ne7 47. Nf7+ Kg6 48. Nxg5 $18) 46. Nxb6 Nf5 47. d5 Ne3+ (47... Nh6+ 48. Kf3 exd5 49. Nxd5 $18) 48. Kf3 $18) 42. d5 Ke7 (42... exd5 43. exd5 Nd6 44. Nxd6 Kxd6 45. Kd4 Ke7 46. Ke5 $18) 43. Kf4 Nd6 44. Nxb6 exd5 45. exd5 f6 (45... Nf5 46. Ke5 Nh4 47. d6+ Kd8 48. Nc4 $18 (48. Kf6 $18)) 46. gxf6+ Kxf6 47. Nd7+ Ke7 48. Ne5 Kf6 49. Ng4+ Ke7 50. b6 g5+ (50... Nb7 51. Ke5 Nd6 52. Ne3 Nb7 (52... g5 53. Nf5+ $18) 53. Nc4 Nc5 54. d6+ Kd7 55. Kd5 Nxa4 56. b7 Nc3+ 57. Ke5 $18) 51. Kxg5 Nb7 52. Ne3 Kd6 53. Kf6 Nc5 (53... Kc5 54. Ke7 Kxb6 55. d6 Nc5 56. d7 Nxd7 (56... Nb7 57. d8=Q+ (57. Nf5 $18) 57... Nxd8 58. Kxd8 Kc5 59. Nd1 Kc4 60. Nb2+ Kb3 61. Kc7 Kxb2 62. Kb6 $18) 57. Kxd7 Kc5 58. Nd1 Kb4 59. Nb2 Kb3 60. Kc6 Kxb2 61. Kb5 Kc3 62. Kxa5 Kc4 63. Kb6 $18) 54. Kf7 Nd7 55. b7 Ne5+ 56. Ke8 Kc7 57. d6+ Kxb7 58. d7 Nxd7 59. Kxd7 Kb6 60. Kd6 1-0

