1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 c6 4. e4 dxe4 (4... Bb4 $6 5. cxd5 exd5 6. e5 $1 $14 Ne7 7. Nf3 c5 8. a3 Ba5 9. dxc5 $16) 5. Nxe4 Bb4+ 6. Nc3 $5 {This is a good way to avoid the main theoretical lines and go for a slight advantage!} c5 (6... e5 $5 7. a3 Bxc3+ (7... Ba5 8. Be3 (8. dxe5 $5 {Capturing on e5 may be also playable, but 8.Be3 is better.} Qxd1+ 9. Kxd1 Bf5 10. f4 $132) 8... exd4 9. Qxd4 Qxd4 10. Bxd4 Nf6 11. O-O-O Be6 12. Nh3 $1 $14 (12. Nf3 $14)) 8. bxc3 Qa5 (8... Nf6 9. Nf3 e4 (9... exd4 10. cxd4 O-O 11. Be3 $14) 10. Ne5 $14) 9. Bd2 Nf6 10. Nf3 Bg4 11. Be2 Nbd7 (11... e4 12. Ne5 $16) 12. O-O e4 13. Ne1 Bxe2 14. Qxe2 O-O 15. Nc2 $14) 7. a3 $1 Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 Nf6 9. Nf3 Nc6 (9... Qa5 $1 {This might be the only good move for Black.} 10. Bd2 Ne4 11. Bd3 Nxd2 12. Qxd2 cxd4 (12... O-O $1 13. Qc2 h6 14. O-O $14) 13. cxd4 Qxd2+ 14. Kxd2 Nd7 15. a4 $1 $16 {White wants to play a4-a5 and fix Black's queenside pawns, regardless if Black plays b6 or not. White can also continue with Rhb1 and Kc3 or Ke3 later.}) (9... O-O $6 10. Bd3 Nbd7 11. O-O b6 12. Ne5 $16) (9... b6 $6 10. Bd3 Bb7 11. O-O O-O 12. Re1 $16) 10. Be2 Qa5 (10... O-O 11. O-O {White wants to continue with Bg5 next. If Black's c6-knight was on d7, then Bg5 won't do much as the knight on f6 would be protected by his colleague, but here, the pin would be annoying and it's a bit difficult to get rid of it.} Ne4 {This is premature.} (11... h6 {This may be Black's best move, preventing Bg5.} 12. Bf4 {White has an advantage with a very comfortable position.} (12. Ne5 {This move should also be considered.})) 12. Qc2 $16) 11. O-O Ne4 (11... Qxc3 12. Ra2 {White is threatening to trap the queen with Bd2.} Nxd4 (12... Qa5 13. d5 $16) 13. Nxd4 Qxd4 14. Rd2 $18) 12. d5 Nxc3 13. Qd2 Nxe2+ 14. Qxe2 Ne7 15. Bb2 ({Another possibility is:} 15. dxe6 Bxe6 16. Qe5 O-O-O 17. Bg5 $14) 15... O-O 16. dxe6 fxe6 17. Qe5 Rf7 18. Qh5 Qc7 19. Rad1 g6 20. Qe5 Qxe5 21. Nxe5 Rf8 22. Rfe1 Nf5 23. Rd3 Nh6 24. Red1 Nf7 25. Nxf7 Kxf7 26. Be5 Kg8 27. Rd8 b6 28. Rxf8+ Kxf8 29. Rd8+ Kf7 30. h4 h6 31. g4 1-0

